{
  "modelName": "Coffee_Model_V3_FunctionalDomain",
  "modelDescription": "Functional-domain decomposition of coffee making and consumption. Entities are organized into eight functional domains: WaterPreparationDomain, BeanStorageAndGrindingDomain, EspressoBrewingDomain (deep decomposition of internal machine components), ManualBrewingDomain (pour over, French press, Aeropress, Moka pot, cold brew, siphon), MilkTexturingDomain, ServingAndConsumptionDomain, MaintenanceDomain, and MeasurementDomain. Cross-domain Associations connect water supply to brewers, grinders to brew methods, and brew output to serving vessels.",
